OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fincreasingly bright end to the
OL,7,Fafternoon, with sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping this evening. Plenty of
OL,9,Fclear spells developing overnight. It
OL,10,Fwill be a warm and humid night, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures remaining in double
OL,12,Ffigures.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,15,Fwith plenty of sunny spells. A small
OL,16,Fchance of a few light showers later in
OL,17,Fthe afternoon. Feeling hot and
OL,18,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
