OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FTurning very hot and humid next week
OL,7,Fwith warm and muggy nights. Largely
OL,8,Fdry with strong sunshine and just a
OL,9,Fsmall chance of a few showers on
OL,10,FMonday.
